{"tid":1790332,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"電玩中的多樣香港：由像素化霓虹燈牌，到香港抗爭題材","createTime":"2019-12-20T02:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T07:23:00.000Z","uid":321748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e085a61212f2f1df5eafb956c74a39d3fb71d3","tid":1790332,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://stories.mplus.org.hk/tc/blog/the-many-video-game-versions-of-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.mplus.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fblog%2Fthe-many-video-game-versions-of-hong-kong&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5R5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=eaeb463a\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.mplus.org.hk/tc/blog/the-many-video-game-versions-of-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n內文收錄與媒體學者兼藝術家戴修的對談，探討電子遊戲中描繪的香港，由1980年代早期遊戲中的像素化霓虹燈牌，談到當下以香港抗爭者為題材的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Y9rj4lr5WWQ/XfuEqQ7CsBI/AAAAAAAAGiY/x0crLjbcrhALqPGrJCMzuy4defbTK3I4wCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/mplusblogpost.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Y9rj4lr5WWQ%2FXfuEqQ7CsBI%2FAAAAAAAAGiY%2Fx0crLjbcrhALqPGrJCMzuy4defbTK3I4wCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs1600%2Fmplusblogpost.png&h=8f77f5cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df0ddc51329b035323d313ac444b8113beef553c","tid":1790332,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T02:20:32.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲都係最好嘅做Game題材"},{"pid":"faaec5db8f787d2a54d6acb3bd33574c70fcd45f","tid":1790332,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"最正係古惑仔1<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4e85d95955ee0182d219eefaf3ff4cd5ac214a","tid":1790332,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"Sleeping Dog<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fe34b456fc429fcdff1f838e56c8f110c91bdc","tid":1790332,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0